description:
This is a 11 minute workout called 'A Deeper Connection with Your Higher Self  (Guided Meditation)' from the channel Great Meditation.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Deep Recharge and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This is an Original 10 minute guided meditation recorded by us.  As the world awakens, may you align your thoughts, your actions, and your intentions with the purest essence of your being.  Let love be your compass, guiding you towards compassion, kindness, and joy.  Embrace the truth that you are a vessel of divine light, here to illuminate the path for yourself and others.  Take a moment to reflect on your dreams, your aspirations, and the miracles that await you.  Visualize yourself stepping into the grand tapestry of your purpose, embracing every step with grace and courage.  Trust in the wisdom of your higher self, for it holds the keys to unlock the infinite possibilities that lie before you.

Today, as you navigate the ebb and flow of life's currents, remember to seek stillness within.  Find solace in the depths of your being, where your intuition whispers ancient truths and your spirit dances to the rhythm of the universe.

A special thank you to all our monthly supporters!
